Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.61,0:16:53.70,InSong-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\1vc(&H825D01&,&HF64EAA&,&H4174D1&,&H000C7B&)}邁開腳步吧 就在我們縱身一躍
